frontend : 

    -> npm i create vite@latest : for react
    -> npm i axios react-router-dom react-toastify
    -> npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer : add tailwindcss
                            -> npx tailwindcss init -p
                            -> ( /** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
                                export default {
                                content: [
                                    "./index.html",
                                    "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
                                ],
                                theme: {
                                    extend: {},
                                },
                                plugins: [],
                                }
                            )
                            paste : index.css
                            -> @tailwind base;
                               @tailwind components;
                               @tailwind utilities;

Backend                           
-> npm i express mongoose multer bcrypt dotenv cors cloudinary jsonwebtoken nodemon validator
-> npm install razorpay for online payment method
->started:npm run server


